    <name>George "Tex" Barringer</name>
    <description><![CDATA[marker pending | thc:Latitude/Longitude is a general geocoded approximation from the street address (US Census geocoder), not field-verified.<br/><br/><b>Address:</b> 1400 9th St, Wichita Falls<br/><br/><b>Marker Text:</b> marker pending]]></description>
