    <description><![CDATA[<b>⚠ PENDING — marker may not yet be installed at this location.</b><br/><br/>on the west side of the entry door to the Wichita Falls Regional Airport<br/><br/><b>Address:</b> 4000 Armstrong Dr., Wichita Falls]]></description>
    <Point><coordinates>-98.489897,33.96612,0</coordinates></Point>
